{"tid":931273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"都叫你班窮撚咪學人食自助餐【生蠔附送蟲蟲】","createTime":"2018-12-07T02:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T03:54:40.000Z","uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d76e53b4b7a9ffd436e2615aba118685b3807b3","tid":931273,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/bkn-20181207073033913-1207_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181207%2Fbkn-20181207073033913-1207_00822_001.html&d=RGtujUXDJSHD%2FDnQ12ZO07IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d5429384\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/bkn-20181207073033913-1207_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n條LINK有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>自助餐吃生蠔　附送生猛蟲蟲　進食係咪有害？</strong><br />\n<br />\n進食任何刺身或生的貝殼類食物，均存在一定風險。近日有食客在進食生蠔時，發現了一條活蹦亂跳的啡色蟲蟲，嚇到大驚失色！<br />\n<br />\n影片於星期三（5日）上載至Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」，事發地點為一間提供自助餐服務的扒房。事主發現，餐碟上的生蠔殼中，有一條幼長的啡色蟲蟲不停蠕動，非常生猛！發貼者提醒：「大家食自助餐要睇清楚先」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，該扒房於去年1月曾發生2宗懷疑食物中毒事件，據本網早前報道，多名食客於該扒房的銅鑼灣分店進餐後，先後出現嘔吐、腹瀉、腹痛和發燒等病徵。所有受影響人士均曾進食刺身及生蠔。<br />\n<br />\n據澳門食品安全中心網頁資訊顯示，生蠔上的常見寄生蟲是海洋蠕蟲，多棲身於蠔殼凹凹凸凸的坑洞，有機會在脫殼過程中掉落或被蠔刀推到蠔肉上。雖然蠕蟲不會傷害蠔，暫時亦未有研究指蠕蟲對人類健康構成風險，但建議任何海產均煮熟食用。<br />\n<br />\n本港食物安全中心提醒，生蠔的生長環境容易受病原體及化學污染物污染，進食受污染的生蠔有機會引致食物中毒，建議市民應光顧可靠的持牌店舖，長者、幼童、孕婦和免疫力較弱者應避免進食生蠔。<br />\n<br />\n《港呢啲》向涉事餐廳了解事件，正候回覆。"},{"pid":"5ce33ce9b44817ebd5f9d7ec09d03ad786b014fc","tid":931273,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWyVWkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWyVWkN.jpg&h=c559bffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e3fafa1df7b030e0d6e47b82cad3af554db861e","tid":931273,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"有蟲先新鮮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c7a26a3543d7969053cd6e7898e6c3ef165379","tid":931273,"uid":29523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"段片個配樂做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43e4ecae3031516728fe64c383ae334aef4c3da","tid":931273,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:23:31.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c9a0baa0c44b2ef813e027645375f6c2675c16","tid":931273,"uid":144063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:27:52.000Z","msg":"冇蟲食黎做咩"},{"pid":"103047ef9390027539050331a47db8a84a484357","tid":931273,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:54:08.000Z","msg":"好生猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf6d681c88139822c56bd049bcd6ceff5b1d200","tid":931273,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38c9a0baa0c44b2ef813e027645375f6c2675c16","tid":931273,"uid":144063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:27:52.000Z","msg":"冇蟲食黎做咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"hoball ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識食就一定剩食蟲"}]}